# Rules for Skazmor Project

## Documentation Maintenance
- **ALWAYS** update `memory-bank/gameMechanics.md` when modifying game logic, rules, or mechanics in the code (especially `gameReducer.ts`).
- **ALWAYS** update `memory-bank/gameContent.md` when adding or modifying game content (cards, monsters, spells, abilities).
- **ALWAYS** consult `memory-bank/uiDesign.md` when creating UI and update it when changing the design system.
- Keep documentation in Russian as per user preference.

## Language
- Communicate in Russian.

